      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Translation              : Designed for students with a good working knowledge of Spanish, the course provides training in translation techniques from Spanish into French. Topics will cover areas of a general nature as well as business and administrative texts.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:              There are no professors associated with this course for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

    
      </div>

