                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/cctr-340" class="program-course-title">
              CCTR 340 Introduction to Spanish Text Revision (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-19754" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Translation &amp; Written Comm. (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/619">School of Continuing Studies</a>)</p>
